      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://cycycy5464.github.io/cc408/docs/data-structure/ch03-string/string-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;本章可能在选择题中出现，掌握 KMP 算法的思想，能够手工模拟 KMP 过程即可。&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内存管理概念</title>
